org.elasticsearch.cluster.routing.allocation

Class AllocationExplanation

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.elasticsearch.cluster.routing.allocation.AllocationExplanation
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Streamable

    public class AllocationExplanation
extends Object
implements Streamable
    Instances of this class keeps explanations of decisions that have been made by allocation. An AllocationExplanation consists of a set of per node explanations. Since AllocationExplanation.NodeExplanations are related to shards an AllocationExplanation maps a shards id to a set of AllocationExplanation.NodeExplanations.
